55
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,919
[SPEAKER_00] Načinski su nekad imali u striptizetu.

56
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:17,600
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam.

57
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:22,639
[SPEAKER_01] Mi se razlikujemo, ne bi bilo fair da smo isti.

58
00:04:22,959 --> 00:04:23,920
[SPEAKER_01] Rekla je da je ovo uvod.

59
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:24,959
[SPEAKER_01] A poslije...

60
00:04:25,439 --> 00:04:27,519
[SPEAKER_00] Poslije je poštar vatrogasac, šta je poslije?

61
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:28,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo i ovaj.

62
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:29,600
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

63
00:04:31,439 --> 00:04:32,480
[SPEAKER_00] Kakve odazive na to?

64
00:04:32,959 --> 00:04:33,360
[SPEAKER_01] Odličan.

65
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,920
[SPEAKER_01] Da, super su to cure prihvatile.

66
00:04:36,959 --> 00:04:38,720
[SPEAKER_00] Idu i na račka sima za to.

67
00:04:38,879 --> 00:04:39,519
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je, tako je, da.

68
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:43,040
[SPEAKER_01] Pa imali smo dosta i muškaraca.

69
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:48,879
[SPEAKER_01] Zapravo oni ono, čak i najbolje su nacrtali od svih jer oni nekako su smireni.

70
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:49,759
