94
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:50,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ojoj, a temu, kad se nađete, dobro, koji izabire vino?

95
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:53,199
[SPEAKER_01] Koji izabire vino?

96
00:05:53,839 --> 00:05:56,240
