[SPEAKER_01] E, kako ko?

114
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:42,959
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se prilagodim.

115
00:06:43,839 --> 00:06:44,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ja kao podupirem.

116
00:06:45,199 --> 00:06:48,879
[SPEAKER_01] A gledite, ako im se tresu ruke, pa treba malo popcini.

117
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,560
