118
00:06:50,879 --> 00:06:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ne, to nam pomose doma.

119
00:06:52,319 --> 00:06:53,199
[SPEAKER_00] Pa propagiraj sve.

120
00:06:54,240 --> 00:07:02,240
