122
00:07:04,639 --> 00:07:05,759
[SPEAKER_00] Moja je već obješena jedna.

123
00:07:06,079 --> 00:07:06,959
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam ni sumnjao, ja.

124
00:07:07,279 --> 00:07:08,399
[SPEAKER_00] Tako nisam ni sumnjao.

125
00:07:09,519 --> 00:07:11,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ali vi ste i vi najbolje fendice, između ostalog.

126
00:07:11,839 --> 00:07:13,279
